# LaTeX用法

## 基本语法

* Comment: %
* Comamnd: 
  \cmd{param0}, cmd act in {...}
  {\cmd ...}, cmd act in {...}
* Environment:
  \begin{env}
  content in env
  \end{env}
* Parameters:
  if in [...], it's optional
  if in {...}, it's reqired
  \cmd[opt1, opt2, opt3]{param1, param2, param3}
  
## 环境

确定表格在文中的位置

  \begin{table}[htb!]
  
## 文章结构

article
  title
  tableofcontents
  section
    subsection
      subsubsection
        paragraph
          subparagraph

## 表格

符号 | 表示是否在左右加上框

  \begin{tabular}{c|c|c}

\begin{table}[htb!]
  \begin{tabular}{l|l}
    \hline File & Description\\
    \hline
  \end{tabular}
\end{table}

## 添加ASCII图片

注意使用等款字体

  \lstset{frame=none}
  \begin{lstlisting}
  /-----------------\
  | Things to do    |
  | o Cut the grass |
  | o Buy jam       |
  | o Fix car       |
  | o Make website  |
  \-----------------/
  \end{lstlisting}

